text: Eveliina Summanen (born 29 May 1998) is a Finnish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Finland women's national team. ==Career== Summanen has been capped for the Finland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish women's footballers Category:Finland women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:KIF Örebro DFF players Category:HJK Helsinki (women) players
